{"tid":1902230,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"自大冇料同事","createTime":"2020-02-28T08:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T10:40:01.000Z","uid":235085,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9d7fd106edd920df32d93dfaa25d8df9b06e87","tid":1902230,"uid":235085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"屌拿星<br />\n有冇人遇過冇料但又自大既同事<br />\n<br />\n我地trainee要做project<br />\n條友話自己讀marketing對公司IT product唔熟<br />\n但係就好自願做group leader report比老細聽<br />\n<br />\n跟住第一次同老細開會 老細講明左想要咩 要我地搵下呢排既trend同整個新solution處理賣<br />\n<br />\n好啦 開完會要分工 條友超大聲講<br />\n「我其實好唔鍾意做group project 鍾意自己做多d」<br />\n我地成group個陣冇為意<br />\n點知條友自己dup左份ppt出黎 將我地講既keywords就咁擺曬落去 但係9唔搭8<br />\n<br />\n好啦我地想汁好d 內容 <br />\n佢就發老脾話唔準改佢d野 如果我地要加野就擺appendix<br />\nLOL DLLM呢個係group project唔係individual project 你條友唔識IT野 又要攬曬上身<br />\n我地比意見你就當耳邊風<br />\n<br />\n最後佢report比老細聽既野完全唔係我地傾過既內容<br />\n老細就獨自搵佢傾左陣 但係我地就完全唔知後續係點 問極個group leader都唔覆message但係下個禮拜present <br />\n<br />\n唉 都唔知佢係咪想攬炒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441ba454138338b0345f51b6a1615117b379d018","tid":1902230,"uid":17641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:44:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲人先有料，一人之力玩鳩死你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7261ecc1c130e77ac3414a998c58c80e09b68b1e","tid":1902230,"uid":38030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"唔撚理佢,你哋自己再做一份"},{"pid":"81caea63166f0cb69ff850747612d1353d811249","tid":1902230,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"441ba454138338b0345f51b6a1615117b379d018","tid":1902230,"uid":17641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:44:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲人先有料，一人之力玩鳩死你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"